{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 COMBINED SPECIFICATION: SYSTEM AND METHOD FOR BIO-ACOUSTIC PEPTIDE SYNTHESIS (PHX-01)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 {\b Inventor:} Casey Canfield\line {\b Node:} 1501-P / Panama Lane\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 1. ABSTRACT\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 A system and method for high-purity synthesis of pharmaceutical-grade peptides (PHX-01) using a five-wave acoustic cluster (20Hz\u8211-12.44kHz) and AI-driven panoptic segmentation (YOLOv12+ViT) for real-time biosecurity.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 2. CLAIMS\par}
